title: Grateful Dead Live at Park West Ski Resort on 1983-09-04
description:
Set 1

Bertha-> Promised Land, Friend Of The Devil, Little Red Rooster, Tennessee Jed, My Brother Esau, Althea-> Hell In A Bucket, China Cat Sunflower-> I Know You Rider

Set 2

Scarlet Begonias-> Fire On The Mountain, Women Are Smarter-> Drums-> Spanish Jam-> The Wheel-> The Other One-> Wharf Rat-> Around & Around-> One More Saturday Night*, E: U.S. Blues

*One More Labor Day Night

reviews.review_text: Decent Show and Recording Note that the track listing is off - Man Smart, Woman Smarter is after Fire and is listed as Drums.
